社局事业单位人事管理科工作人员接受采访时说，41名事业单位人员“上岸”后被集体清退...当地回应_腾讯新闻"},"attached_info":"CkAI4evn7vOsle9GEAMaCTEwOTk0OTcyMCDrsoC2BjAAOPIDQAJyCTY2NDUyNTE4NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"478 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b42615c30c2b7a9cbe81ca989de639af_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1723897389.405327","card_id":"Q_664464076","target":{"id":664464076,"title":"如何评价吴艳妮飞速接到新代言，她的商业价值真的这么高吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664464076","type":"question","created":1723801836,"answer_count":140,"follower_count":184,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1538,19487,25049,1344967,2878898],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI4evn7vOsle9GEAMaCTEwOTkzNjIxMiDswfy1BjAAOLgBQANyCTY2NDQ2NDA3NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"133 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3056a165640d3b9998a30ce3f34bf0c7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1723897389.406409","card_id":"Q_664483968","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":664483968,"title":"知友爆料有蚁商向达州神龙洞投毒，这类珍稀却不在「名录」的生物保护，目前面临着哪些困境？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664483968","type":"question","created":1723816759,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":99,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5082,49497,89475,362157,2021862],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"针对这类物种保护，有什么亟需解决的问题？ 来源指路：如何看待网友爆料某蚁商为垄断在达州神龙溶洞栖息的具有重要价值的穴胫步甲，而在神龙洞进行了大量投毒？"},"attached_info":"Cj